title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2015 - San Diego, CA, USA
description:
Come spend the Global Day of Code with Pluralsight in Little Italy, San Diego, CA 
Light Breakfast (Bruegger's Bagels, Muffins, Coffee and Juice) 
Lunch (Buca di Beppo Main Dishes/Pasta and Salad) provided. 
* We are on the second floor; building does not have an elevator. Parking is available in the Ace parking lot for $10-$15 ( 2265 India St, San Diego CA 92101) or  paidstreet parking for 2 hours
